@graph.content: The technology can be used to locate people or animals in case of natural disaster.
The technology can be used to watch the flight patterns of baseballs when thrown by pitchers.
The technology can be used to observe bird populations in different biomes.
The technology can be used to observe the motion of waves in an attempt to explain the rogue wave phenomenon.
The technology can be used to observe lights in the night sky.
The technology can be used to observe changes in movement of humans due to injury.
